[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Container overflow:      fc[0m                                                       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mINFO:__main__:Running: docker run --privileged --shm-[0m[33msize[0m[39m=[0m[35m2g[0m[39m --platform linux/amd64[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m--rm -i -e [0m[33mHELPER[0m[39m=[0m[3;92mTrue[0m[39m -e [0m[33mARCHITECTURE[0m[39m=[0m[35mx86_64[0m[39m -v [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/home/user/crete/packages/python_oss_fuzz/.oss_fuzz/build/out/[0m[95mlibexif[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mout[0m[39m -v [0m      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexif_from_data_fuzzer -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mWhen running the `exif_from_data_fuzzer` against a crafted input, AddressSanitizer [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreports a heap-buffer-overflow in the `exif_data_load_data_entry` function of [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibexif. A [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-byte read exceeds a [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m-byte allocated buffer, leading to an [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimmediate abort.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Issue type: Heap-based buffer overflow [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmulti-byte read past allocated region[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Trigger: The fuzzer invokes `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput`, which calls [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_new_from_data`. This leads into a chain of functions in [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`libexif/exif-data.c`:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. `exif_data_new_from_data`[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. `exif_data_load_data`[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. `exif_data_load_data_content`[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. `exif_data_load_data_entry`  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `exif_data_load_data_entry` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlibexif/exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:213[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, a call to `memcpy` [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreads [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bytes starting exactly at the end of a heap buffer that was allocated with[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m207[0m[39m bytes. AddressSanitizer identifies this as a heap-buffer-overflow.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Key log excerpt:[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ````  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  READ of size [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m at [0m[1;36m0x51100000024f[0m[39m  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m0x51100000024f[0m[39m is located [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m bytes after [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m-byte region [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m[[0m[1;36m0x511000000180[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m0x51100000024f[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  SUMMARY: AddressSanitizer: heap-buffer-overflow … exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:213:3[0m[39m in [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexif_data_load_data_entry  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ````[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Important observations:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The overflow occurs during parsing of EXIF data entries, specifically when [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcopying entry data.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The vulnerable path is exercised by the fuzz harness but the root cause resides[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min the core parsing functions of libexif.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The buffer in question is allocated earlier in the call chain before [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry` is invoked.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Code areas for further investigation:[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • `libexif/exif-data.c`, around line [0m[1;36m213[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`exif_data_load_data_entry`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrelated functions at lines ~[0m[1;36m531[0m[39m, ~[0m[1;36m984[0m[39m, ~[0m[1;36m159[0m[39m.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Memory allocation logic preceding the vulnerable `memcpy`, to confirm buffer [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msizing.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The fuzzer entry point in `exif_from_data_fuzzer.cc` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m51[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munderstand how input size and content map to parsing routines.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Any bounds checks or length calculations in EXIF data entry headers.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m206[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m  [0m[32m"Tag data goes past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%u > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdoff+s, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m207[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m208[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m209[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m210[0m[39m:    [0m[39mentry->data = exif_data_alloc [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m211[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m212[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mentry->size = s;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m213[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mmemcpy [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m214[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m215[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mEXIF_LOG_NO_MEMORY[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m216[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m217[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m218[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m219[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* If this is the MakerNote, remember the offset *[0m[35m/[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m220[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->tag == EXIF_TAG_MAKER_NOTE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m221[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!entry->data[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibexif/exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:959[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m984[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m959[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Byte order [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, length [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m960[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!memcmp [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, [0m[32m"II"[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m961[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mdata->priv->order = EXIF_BYTE_ORDER_INTEL;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m962[0m[39m:    [0m[39melse if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!memcmp [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, [0m[32m"MM"[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m963[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mdata->priv->order = EXIF_BYTE_ORDER_MOTOROLA;[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m964[0m[39m:    [0m[39melse [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m965[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_CORRUPT_DATA,[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m966[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m  [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m, [0m[1;35m_[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Unknown encoding."[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m967[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m968[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m969[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m970[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Fixed value *[0m[35m/[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m971[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mexif_get_short [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m != [0m[1;36m0x002a[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m972[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m973[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m974[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* IFD [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m offset *[0m[35m/[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m975[0m[39m:    [0m[39moffset = exif_get_long [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m976[0m[39m:    [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m, [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m977[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m  [0m[32m"IFD 0 at %i."[0m[39m, [0m[1;39m([0m[39mint[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m978[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m979[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* ds is restricted to [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bit above, so offset is restricted too, and [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moffset+[0m[1;36m8[0m[39m should not overflow. *[0m[35m/[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m980[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset > ds || offset + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m > ds[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m981[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m982[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m983[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Parse the actual exif data [0m[1;39m([0m[39musually offset [0m[1;36m14[0m[39m from start[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m984[0m[39m:    [0m[39mexif_data_load_data_content [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, EXIF_IFD_0, d + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, ds - [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, offset, [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Locate and strengthen the bounds‐checking in exif_data_load_data_entry:[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In libexif/exif-data.c around line [0m[1;36m198[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m207[0m[39m, instead of the two separate guards[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff >= size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > size - doff[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     introduce a single, overflow‐safe check before memcpy:[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Combined, integer‐overflow‐safe bounds check *[0m[35m/[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39munsigned long[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mdoff + [0m[1;39m([0m[39munsigned long[0m[1;39m)[0m[39ms > [0m[1;39m([0m[39munsigned long[0m[1;39m)[0m[39msize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    [0m[32m"Tag data goes past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32moffset+[0m[32msize[0m[32m=%u > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m,[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    doff + s, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This ensures that any request to copy `s` bytes from offset `doff` into the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap buffer which may have been truncated or shifted upstream is rejected, and also[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mguarantees that `doff+s` cannot wrap around the unsigned boundary undetected.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Maintain the existing `exif_data_alloc` and `memcpy` logic unaltered, so valid [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentries are still processed as before.[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Do **not** modify the fuzzer harness, test code, or any external dependencies. [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAll changes are confined to the core parsing function in libexif.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Rationale:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The AddressSanitizer report shows a [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-byte read exactly at the end of a [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m207[0m[39m-byte buffer—i.e., `doff + s == size`. The original two checks can, under [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcertain pointer-shift or [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m‐bit truncation scenarios, slip past one guard but still[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverflow on `memcpy`.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A single `doff + s > size` check is both simpler and robust against unsigned [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwrap‐around. It preserves the intended behavior of dropping corrupt entries rather [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthan copying out‐of‐bounds.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This approach follows the existing style of sanity‐checking corrupt EXIF data [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand logging a debug message, and it will prevent heap‐buffer‐overflows without [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maltering any downstream logic.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects:[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Malformed entries whose `doff + s` precisely equals or exceeds the truncated [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer length will now be skipped, as before intended. Applications relying on [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msubtly out‐of‐bounds reads [0m[1;39m([0m[39mundefined behavior[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m will no longer see that data, but [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthis is desirable for safety.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No existing test or legitimate EXIF parsing path is changed, since well‐formed[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtags always satisfy `doff + s <= size`.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Verification:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run `exif_from_data_fuzzer` under AddressSanitizer to confirm that the [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap‐buffer‐overflow no longer reproduces.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Execute the full libexif test suite and existing OSS-Fuzz targets to ensure no[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mregressions.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverflow occurring at the updated code location [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset by a few lines[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. No new [0m    [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A fuzzing session on `exif_from_data_fuzzer` triggered an ASan error in  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     `exif_data_load_data_entry` [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:213[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The overflow read [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bytes at address `[0m[1;36m0x51100000024f[0m[39m`, which is immediately [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbeyond a [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m-byte region allocated at `[0m[1;36m0x511000000180[0m[39m`.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Call stack highlights:  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • `exif_data_load_data_entry` → `exif_data_load_data_content` → [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data` → `exif_data_new_from_data` → fuzzer harness.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No other errors or different backtraces were reported.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Original code [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m194[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Sanity checks *[0m[35m/[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff >= size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m … [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > size - doff[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m … [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Patched code:[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Sanity checks *[0m[35m/[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39munsigned long[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mdoff + [0m[1;39m([0m[39munsigned long[0m[1;39m)[0m[39ms > [0m[1;39m([0m[39munsigned long[0m[1;39m)[0m[39msize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[39m, [0m[32m"Tag data goes past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32moffset+[0m[32msize[0m[32m=%u > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdoff+s, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The two discrete checks were collapsed into one that guards the sum `doff + s`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39magainst `size`.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Post-Patch Result  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Fuzzer re-ran under ASan, hitting the same overflow in [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnow at line [0m[1;36m208[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The log is nearly identical: a [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-byte read past the same [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m-byte region.  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This confirms the combined check did not prevent the out-of-bounds memcpy.[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Further Investigation  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   To understand and fix the underlying overflow, review:  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Calculation of `doff` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe data offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: how `offset` and the header size [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m8[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are determined.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Computation of `s` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe data length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: how EXIF tag types and counts translate [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto byte sizes.  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Any integer overflows or signed/unsigned mismatches in `doff + s`.  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The sequence in `exif_data_load_data_content` and `exif_data_load_data` that [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mleads into the entry loader.  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Edge cases where tags specify lengths that wrap or exceed the buffer when [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcombined with base offsets.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m374[0m[39m:    static const double log_1_1 = [0m[1;36m0.09531017980432493[0m[39m;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m375[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m376[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Adding [0m[1;36m0.1[0m[39m protects against the case where [0m[33mn[0m[39m==[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m377[0m[39m:    [0m[39mreturn [0m[1;35mceil[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlog[0m[1;39m([0m[39mn + [0m[1;36m0.1[0m[1;39m)[0m[35m/[0m[95mlog_1_1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m378[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m379[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m380[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[39m*! Load data for an IFD.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m381[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m382[0m[39m: * \param[0m[1;39m[[0m[39min,out[0m[1;39m][0m[39m data #ExifData[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m383[0m[39m: * \param[0m[1;39m[[0m[39min[0m[1;39m][0m[39m ifd IFD to load[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m384[0m[39m: * \param[0m[1;39m[[0m[39min[0m[1;39m][0m[39m d pointer to buffer containing raw IFD data[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m385[0m[39m: * \param[0m[1;39m[[0m[39min[0m[1;39m][0m[39m ds size of raw data in buffer at \c d[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m386[0m[39m: * \param[0m[1;39m[[0m[39min[0m[1;39m][0m[39m offset offset into buffer at \c d at which IFD starts[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m387[0m[39m: * \param[0m[1;39m[[0m[39min[0m[1;39m][0m[39m recursion_cost factor indicating how expensive this recursive[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m388[0m[39m: * call could be[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m389[0m[39m: *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m390[0m[39m:static void[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m391:e[0m[39mxif_data_load_data_content [0m[1;39m([0m[39mExifData *data, ExifIfd ifd,[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m392[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m     const unsigned char *d,[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m393[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m     unsigned int ds, unsigned int offset, unsigned int [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecursion_cost[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m394[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m395[0m[39m:    [0m[39mExifLong o, thumbnail_offset = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, thumbnail_length = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m396[0m[39m:    [0m[39mExifShort n;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m397[0m[39m:    [0m[39mExifEntry *entry;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m398[0m[39m:    [0m[39munsigned int i;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m399[0m[39m:    [0m[39mExifTag tag;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m400[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m401[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!data || !data->priv[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m402[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m403[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m404[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* check for valid ExifIfd enum range *[0m[35m/[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m405[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mint[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mifd[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m < [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[1;39m([0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mint[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mifd[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m >= EXIF_IFD_COUNT[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m406[0m[39m:    [0m[39m  return;[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m407[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m408[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrecursion_cost > [0m[1;36m170[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m409[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[35m/[0m[39m*[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m410[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * recursion_cost is a logarithmic-scale indicator of how expensive[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthis[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m411[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * recursive call might end up being. It is an indicator of the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdepth of[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m412[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * recursion as well as the potential for worst-case future [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecursive[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m413[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * calls. Since it's difficult to tell ahead of time how often [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecursion[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m414[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * will occur, this assumes the worst by assuming every tag could [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mend up[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m415[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * causing recursion.[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m416[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * The value of [0m[1;36m170[0m[39m was chosen to limit typical EXIF structures to [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m417[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * recursive depth of about [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, but pathological ones [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthose with [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvery[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m418[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * many tags[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to only [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m419[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m420[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_CORRUPT_DATA, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibexif/exif-format.[0m[1;92mc:1[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m74[0m                                                          [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m35[0m[39m:     [0m[39m      ExifMemFreeFunc free_func[0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m36[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m37[0m[39m:     [0m[39mExifMem *mem;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m38[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m39[0m[39m:     [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!alloc_func && !realloc_func[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m40[0m[39m:     [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn NULL;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m41[0m[39m:     [0m[39mmem = alloc_func ? alloc_func [0m[1;39m([0m[39msizeof [0m[1;39m([0m[39mExifMem[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m :[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m42[0m[39m:     [0m[39m        [0m[39m           realloc_func [0m[1;39m([0m[39mNULL, sizeof [0m[1;39m([0m[39mExifMem[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m43[0m[39m:     [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!mem[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return NULL;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m44[0m[39m:     [0m[39mmem->ref_count = [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m45[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m48[0m[39m:     [0m[39mmem->free_func    = free_func;[0m                                              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m50[0m[39m:     [0m[39mreturn mem;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m51[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m54:e[0m[39mxif_mem_ref [0m[1;39m([0m[39mExifMem *mem[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
