[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m68[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m69[0m[39m:     [0m[39mExifDataOption options;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m70[0m[39m:     [0m[39mExifDataType data_type;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m71[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m;[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m72[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m73[0m[39m:static void *[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m74:e[0m[39mxif_data_alloc [0m[1;39m([0m[39mExifData *data, unsigned int i[0m[1;39m)[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m75[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m76[0m[39m:     [0m[39mvoid *d;[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m77[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m78[0m[39m:     [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!data || !i[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m79[0m[39m:     [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn NULL;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m80[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m81[0m[39m:     [0m[39md = exif_mem_alloc [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->mem, i[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m82[0m[39m:     [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39md[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m83[0m[39m:     [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn d;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m84[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m85[0m[39m:     [0m[39mEXIF_LOG_NO_MEMORY [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m, i[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m86[0m[39m:     [0m[39mreturn NULL;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m87[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m88[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m89:E[0m[39mxifMnoteData *[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m90:e[0m[39mxif_data_get_mnote_data [0m[1;39m([0m[39mExifData *d[0m[1;39m)[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m91[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m92[0m[39m:     [0m[39mreturn [0m[1;39m([0m[39md && d->priv[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ? d->priv->md : NULL;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m93[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m94[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m95:E[0m[39mxifData *[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m96:e[0m[39mxif_data_new [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvoid[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m97[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m98[0m[39m:     [0m[39mExifMem *mem = exif_mem_new_default [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m99[0m[39m:     [0m[39mExifData *d = exif_data_new_mem [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmem[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m100[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Overview  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   The persistent overflow stems from subtle gaps in how [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry` and its caller `exif_data_load_data_content` validate [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer bounds before reading entry headers, reading the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m‐byte “data offset” field,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand finally performing the `memcpy`. Although collapsing the two original checks [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minto one `[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff + s > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` condition should, in principle, guard against [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mout‐of‐bounds copies, it does not address two root causes that still allow invalid [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreads:[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m No pre‐check that the [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m-byte directory entry itself lies entirely within the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIFD buffer.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m No explicit check that the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte “offset” field [0m[1;39m([0m[39mat `d + offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m can be[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mread safely.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   As a result, malicious or malformed IFDs can slip past the group‐level [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`CHECKOVERFLOW` guard in `exif_data_load_data_content` but still point `doff` into [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mor beyond the end of the buffer.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Key principles to preserve  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • Do not change fuzz harness or external tests.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • Preserve existing logic for TIFF header parsing, IFD iteration, format‐size [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalculation, and thumbnail loading.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • Use the existing `[0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset, datasize, structsize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` macro where [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mappropriate.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • Maintain the two‐stage model: [0m[1;39m([0m[39ma[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m scan directory entries in [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_content`; [0m[1;39m([0m[39mb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m individually parse/copy each entry in [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry`.  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • Do not modify in‐memory IFD layout logic or unify the buffer pointer `d`; [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msimply strengthen bounds checking.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Detailed patch steps[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA. Strengthen per‐entry range checks in exif_data_load_data_content  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   In the loop over `i` entries, before calling into the entry loader:[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```c[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   size_t entry_off = offset + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m * i;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Ensure the [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m‐byte directory entry header is fully inside ds[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry_off, ds, [0m[1;36m12[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Either break [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno more complete entries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m or continue to next i.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[32m"Entry %u header overruns buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%zu + 12 > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m, skipping rest"[0m[39m, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mi, entry_off, ds[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       break;[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   This prevents any out‐of‐bounds reads of the tag, format, component‐count, or [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe offset field itself.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mB. Harden exif_data_load_data_entry  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   In `static int [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_entry[0m[1;39m([0m[39m…, const unsigned char *d, unsigned int[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize, unsigned int offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`:[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. At the very top, verify the [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m bytes needed to read tag/format/components are [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min‐bounds:[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```c[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset, size, [0m[1;36m8[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   [0m[32m"Entry header overruns buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%u + 8 > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, offset, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Compute `s` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnumber of data bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m exactly as before, but add an overflow [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcheck:[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```c[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      unsigned int unit = [0m[1;35mexif_format_get_size[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->format[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[39munit == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m unknown format[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      size_t s = [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39munit * entry->components;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m catch [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m-bit multiplication overflow[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->components && s [0m[35m/[0m[39m entry->components != unit[0m[1;39m)[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Before reading the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte “external data offset” for `s > [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`, ensure we can [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mread it:[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```c[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      size_t doff;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m We need [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes at d + offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, size, [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                       [0m[32m"Cannot read data‐offset field [0m[32m([0m[32m%u + 8 + 4 > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, offset, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          doff = [0m[1;35mexif_get_long[0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          doff = offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Finally, perform a unified, overflow‐safe check for the actual copy window:[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```c[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Must have doff < size, s <= size ‑ doff[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Using CHECKOVERFLOW [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset, datasize, structsize[0m[1;39m)[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff, size, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   [0m[32m"Tag data overruns buffer [0m[32m([0m[32moffset %u + size %zu > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, doff, s,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. Proceed with `entry->data = [0m[1;35mexif_data_alloc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` and the [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` as before.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By guarding each field‐read [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry header, the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte offset, and the final [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcopy[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with precise checks, we close the window for any malformed directory entry to[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mslip through.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We reuse `CHECKOVERFLOW` to cover three key cases:  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset >= size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstructsize > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset > size - structsize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - These guards are applied at the smallest granularity [0m[1;39m([0m[39mper entry, per field[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrather than rely solely on the group‐level test in the parent loop.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We introduce only local variable changes [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. `size_t s, doff`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, without [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maltering any public APIs or fuzz harness.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The existing logic for legitimate tags, thumbnail loading, recursion limits, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39metc., remains untouched.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Potential side effects and mitigation  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Performance: six additional boundary checks per entry—negligible compared to [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe cost of full EXIF parsing.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Code size: slight increase but well within library goals.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Behavior: malformed EXIFs that previously triggered an ASan abort will now [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreturn from `exif_data_new_from_data` gracefully, dropping the offending tag.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No existing unit tests or fuzz harnesses are modified; all checks are [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minternal.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Validation  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Compile with AddressSanitizer, run `exif_from_data_fuzzer`; confirm no [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap‐buffer‐overflow remains.  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run existing regression tests to ensure no feature regressions.  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Optionally, craft minimal reproducer EXIFs to verify each check path [0m[1;39m([0m[39mheader [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverrun, offset‐field overrun, data‐copy overrun[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. References to existing code  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `CHECKOVERFLOW` usage in `exif_data_load_data_content` for entry‐count and [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mgroup‐level size.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `exif_data_load_data_thumbnail` already uses `CHECKOVERFLOW`—we align the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentry loader to the same pattern.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Overflow check pattern [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`s [0m[35m/[0m[39m components`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is a standard wrap‐check seen in [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mother parts of the codebase [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., level‐cost calculation safeguards[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39miterations.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- During parsing in `exif_data_new_from_data` → `exif_data_load_data` → [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_content` → `exif_data_load_data_entry`, a call to `memcpy` [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreads [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bytes from `d + offset + …` past the end of an allocated [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m-byte buffer. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- ASan’s backtrace shows the offending `__asan_memcpy` at line [0m[1;36m213[0m[39m of [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif-data.c`.  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The region `[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0x511000000180[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m0x51100000024f[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` is allocated, but the code issues a [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmulti-byte read starting at address `[0m[1;36m0x51100000024f[0m[39m`, exactly at the end of that [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mregion.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mImportant Observations  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The overflow is a “multi-byte read” of size [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m, indicating the code copies more [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdata than is actually available.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The problematic allocation happens via `malloc` for the entire EXIF segment, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msized by the input length. No per-entry checks guard the copy of tag data.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- There are no early returns or error logs prior to the memcpy call; the parser [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mproceeds without validating that the entry’s declared data length and offset lie [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithin the allocated buffer.[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Changed the types of local variables `s` and `doff` from `unsigned int` to [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`size_t`.  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inserted a check for the entry header overrunning the buffer:  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```c[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset, size, [0m[1;36m8[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[39m, [0m[32m"Entry header overruns buffer"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Validated `unit = [0m[1;35mexif_format_get_size[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->format[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, returned early on zero, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand added overflow detection on `unit * components`.  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- For entries where `s > [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`, checked that reading the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte data-offset field at [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m` does not exceed the buffer.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Replaced separate “offset ≥ size” and “s > size - doff” checks with a single [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff, size, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In the loop over IFD entries, ensured each [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m-byte entry header fits by checking [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry_off, ds, [0m[1;36m12[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` before accessing its tag.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Result  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After rebuilding and rerunning `exif_from_data_fuzzer -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m`, ASan reports [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe same heap-buffer-overflow at `exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:227[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mformerly [0m[1;36m213[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The backtrace and the shadow-byte map remain unchanged, confirming the patch did [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnot prevent the out-of-bounds read.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The logic in `exif_data_load_data_entry` around the memcpy: confirm that [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdestination, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` is guarded by valid `doff` and `s`.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The definition and correctness of the `CHECKOVERFLOW` macro: ensure it accurately[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdetects all out-of-bounds scenarios [0m[1;39m([0m[39mparticularly when `offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m` or `doff + [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ms` wrap or equal the buffer size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The calculation of `components` and the use of `[0m[1;35mexif_format_get_size[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: verify [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat very large `components` or unexpected `format` values cannot bypass the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverflow checks.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The upstream parsing of the directory structure in `exif_data_load_data_content`,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mespecially how `size` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe total IFD size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and `n` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnumber of entries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are derived:[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39many misinterpretation there could lead to reading beyond `d + size`.  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Adjacent functions and loops in `exif-data.c` that likewise read untrusted data [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithout bounds validation, to get a holistic view of the parsing safety.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHere is the initial issue log of the codebase:[0m                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m224[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->size > [0m[1;36m6[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m225[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log,[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m226[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m       EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m227[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m       [0m[32m"MakerNote found [0m[32m([0m[32m%02x %02x %02x [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m%02x "[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m228[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m       [0m[32m"%02x %02x %02x...[0m[32m)[0m[32m."[0m[39m,[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m229[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m       entry->data[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m, entry->data[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m][0m[39m, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentry->data[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m][0m[39m,[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m230[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m       entry->data[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m3[0m[1;39m][0m[39m, entry->data[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m][0m[39m, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentry->data[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m5[0m[1;39m][0m[39m,[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m231[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m       entry->data[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m6[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m232[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m233[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mdata->priv->offset_mnote = doff;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m234[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m235[0m[39m:    [0m[39mreturn [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m;[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m236[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m237[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m238[0m[39m:static void[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m239:e[0m[39mxif_data_save_data_entry [0m[1;39m([0m[39mExifData *data, ExifEntry *e,[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m240[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m   unsigned char **d, unsigned int *ds,[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibexif/exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:430[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m460[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m430[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m431[0m[39m:    [0m[39mn = exif_get_short [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m432[0m[39m:    [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m433[0m[39m:    [0m[39m          [0m[32m"Loading %hu entries..."[0m[39m, n[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m434[0m[39m:    [0m[39moffset += [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m435[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m436[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Check if we have enough data. *[0m[35m/[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m437[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset, ds, [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m*n[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m438[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mn = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mds - offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m439[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m440[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m  [0m[32m"Short data; only loading %hu entries..."[0m[39m, n[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m441[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m442[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m443[0m[39m:    [0m[39mfor [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < n; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m444[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m445[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mtag = exif_get_short [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m * i, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m446[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mswitch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtag[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m447[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mcase EXIF_TAG_EXIF_IFD_POINTER:[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m448[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mcase EXIF_TAG_GPS_INFO_IFD_POINTER:[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m449[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mcase EXIF_TAG_INTEROPERABILITY_IFD_POINTER:[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m450[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mcase EXIF_TAG_JPEG_INTERCHANGE_FORMAT_LENGTH:[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m451[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mcase EXIF_TAG_JPEG_INTERCHANGE_FORMAT:[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m452[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mo = exif_get_long [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m * i + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m,[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m453[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m   data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m454[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mo >= ds[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m455[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mEXIF_LOG_CODE_CORRUPT_DATA, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m456[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m  [0m[32m"Tag data past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%u > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moffset+[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m, ds[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m457[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m458[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m459[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[35m/[0m[39m* FIXME: IFD_POINTER tags aren't marked as being in a[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m460[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m * specific IFD, so exif_tag_get_name_in_ifd won't work[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Overview of the root cause  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Despite adding `CHECKOVERFLOW` guards, the existing macro and its use in [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry` do not comprehensively prevent out-of-bounds multi-byte[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreads in all corner cases. In particular:[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The entry header check at the top only covers the first [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m bytes, not the full [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m12[0m[39m-byte directory entry.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The logic for small values of `s` [0m[1;39m([0m[39m≤[0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m relies on the [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-byte check plus the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIFD’s [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m-byte check in the caller, which still allows certain malformed offsets to [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mslip through.[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Consolidating two simple bounds checks into one `[0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff, size, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mobscures the actual invariant we need: “any read of N bytes at offset O must [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msatisfy O + N ≤ size.”[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The signature still uses `unsigned int size, offset`, leading to potential [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtype mismatches and inadvertent wrap-around when computing `size − offset`.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Strategy to eliminate the overflow in one shot  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Change local parameters to `size_t` and replace all uses of `CHECKOVERFLOW` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minside `exif_data_load_data_entry` with explicit, per-read subtraction checks of [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe form  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset > size − needed_bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      This directly enforces the invariant `offset + needed_bytes ≤ size` without [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmacro pitfalls.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. At the very top of `exif_data_load_data_entry`, validate the entire [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m-byte [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdirectory entry header in one check.  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   C. After calculating `s = unit * components` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwith overflow already checked[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mperform two distinct checks:  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       – For `s ≤ [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`, confirm that `offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m + s ≤ size`.  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       – For `s  > [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`, confirm first that `offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m ≤ size` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mto read the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdata-offset field[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, then read `doff`, then confirm `doff + s ≤ size`.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   D. Ensure all arithmetic is done in `size_t`, and avoid any unsigned underflow [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mby always checking “size ≥ offset + X” as “offset ≤ size − X.”[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Concrete steps  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   In `libexif/exif-data.c`:[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Change the function signature to[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```c[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      static int[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_entry[0m[1;39m([0m[39mExifData *data,[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                ExifEntry *entry,[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                const unsigned char *d,[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                size_t size,[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                size_t offset[0m[1;39m)[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      and adjust the caller in `exif_data_load_data_content` accordingly [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcast its [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ds` and `offset` to `size_t`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m At the top of `exif_data_load_data_entry`, insert:[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```c[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Must have room for the entire [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m-byte IFD entry header *[0m[35m/[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset > size || size - offset < [0m[1;36m12[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   [0m[32m"Entry header overruns buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%zu + 12 > %zu[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, offset, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Read `tag`, `format`, `components` unconditionally [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthey occupy the first [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes which we know lie within the [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m-byte header[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Compute and sanity-check `s` exactly as in the previous patch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcatching [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmultiplication overflow and `s == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m5[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Split into two cases:[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms <= [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ```c[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         size_t doff = offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[39m* embedded data: ensure we can copy s bytes starting at offset+[0m[1;36m8[0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff > size || size - doff < s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                      [0m[32m"Inline tag data overruns buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%zu + %zu > %zu[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m,[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                      doff, s, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ```[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m `else [0m[35m/[0m[39m* s > [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m[39m`  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ```c[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[39m* ensure we can read the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte data-offset field *[0m[35m/[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m > size || size - [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m < [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                      [0m[32m"Cannot read data-offset field [0m[32m([0m[32m%zu + 4 > %zu[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m,[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                      offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         size_t doff = [0m[1;35mexif_get_long[0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[39m* ensure we can copy s bytes starting at doff *[0m[35m/[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff > size || size - doff < s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                      [0m[32m"External tag data overruns buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%zu + %zu > %zu[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m,[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                      doff, s, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ```[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m6[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Only after these checks allocate `entry->data` and do:[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```c[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Why this approach is optimal  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - It directly enforces the fundamental invariant [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`start + length ≤ size`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m for [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mevery multi-byte access without relying on a complex macro.  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - It handles both inline data [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`s ≤ [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and external data [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`s > [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprecise, separate checks.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Switching to `size_t` for all buffer/offset arithmetic prevents underflow or [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwrap-around anomalies with large values.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - It preserves existing parsing logic and error-handling paths: malformed [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentries still fail early and return `[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m`, letting the parser move on.  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We do not modify any harness, fuzz-logic, or tests. All test-cases that [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexercise valid EXIF data will continue to succeed, and malformed inputs will now be[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msafely skipped without a crash.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Side-effects and mitigation  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Slight reduction in the set of “accepted” malformed directory entries—instead [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof letting borderline cases slip through, we now reject any that do not strictly [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msatisfy `offset + length ≤ size`. This aligns with safe parsing and is acceptable [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min a security-sensitive library.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Performance impact is negligible: a handful of integer compares and [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msubtractions per entry.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This pattern can serve as a template to audit and harden other parts of [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`libexif` that perform unbounded reads.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>libexif/exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:160[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m240[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>libexif/exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:430[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m460[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
